# TypeScript Rules

- Use `npm run` scripts for TypeScript commands.
- Follow the compiler mode configured in `tsconfig.json`.
- Do not add `any`, `// @ts-ignore`, broad casts, or broad suppressions.
- Keep source in `src/` for TypeScript-only projects and `packages/typescript/src/` for monorepos.
- Keep TypeScript validation green before claiming completion.
{% if use_biome %}
- Keep Biome formatting and linting green when TypeScript files change.
{% endif %}
{% if use_vitest %}
- Keep Vitest tests and coverage green when behavior changes.
{% endif %}
